data.description: ****MOTIVATED SELLERS****Spacious Waterfront Home Located on a Freshwater canal, which is Conveniently located in the Heart of Port Charlotte, within a short Drive to everything, Shopping, Dining, Port Charlotte Beach Complex, Charlotte Harbor, Boating, Fishing, Golf, Tennis, Pickleball, Punta Gorda and North Port, Ideal Home to Live the Florida Lifestyle Year around, or that Winter Retreat you are Looking for. This Charming Three (3) Bedroom, Two (2) Bath Home, attached Two (2) Car Garage, with Open Living Space from the Volume Ceilings, Open Floor Plan with step-down Spacious Great Room and Open Kitchen with abundant Cabinetry, Stainless Steel Appliances Expansive Breakfast Bar, tile flooring throughout, Private Owners Suite, the Sliders open up for you to Enjoy the Screened Patio overlooking the Waterfront and Fenced Backyard giving way to More Living Space, plus room to add a Pool if desired. New Shingle Roof as of July 2022. We invite you for a Tour Today.
